###

### Notes
- OTP: the app sends OTP via the configured `IEmailService`. For end-to-end testing you must obtain the OTP from the email sink or mock the OTP service.
- Replace `{{WorkFlow.API_HostAddress}}` and placeholders (`<REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE>`, `{{WORKFLOW_ID}}`) before sending requests.

### Curl / PowerShell examples
# curl (Windows WSL or Git Bash)
curl -X POST "{{WorkFlow.API_HostAddress}}/Auth/Login" \
	-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
	-d '{"type":"email","email":"testuser@gmail.com","password":"P@ssw0rd!"}'

# PowerShell (Windows PowerShell)
Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post -Uri "{{WorkFlow.API_HostAddress}}/Auth/Login" -ContentType "application/json" -Body (@{ type = 'email'; email = 'testuser@gmail.com'; password = 'P@ssw0rd!' } | ConvertTo-Json)

